{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Overview</h2><br>The game is a short walking simulator that explores a 3D space.<br>However, the controlling character is trapped in the Mirror World, and the player must control him from the real world to lead him to the goal.<br><br>The only obstacles in the way of walking are those that exist in the Mirror World. <br>Obstacles in the real world can be ignored. The player must successfully dodge invisible obstacles.<br><br>The controls are first-person, with only movement and the camera as the main controls.<br>No time limit or advanced action controls are required. Take your time and enjoy the exploration!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Game system</h2>\u30fbMirror<br>When you look into the mirror, you can see the world beyond.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870810/extras/kagami.gif?t=1713263537\" /><br>\u30fbButton<br>When you press the button, the mirror appears at the current position.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870810/extras/button.gif?t=1713263537\" /><br>\u30fbGoal<br>Touch the goal to advance to the next stage.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870810/extras/goal.gif?t=1713263537\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"STAGE 1","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2870810/01e1c95b54a0594095f3ebcba23e3212afb3d01d.jpg"},{"name":"STAGE 2","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2870810/a9babdb74869b9b3617a5254a5b3d185251c137e.jpg"},{"name":"STAGE 3","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2870810/3a436284ca309aa8c9f97d4fbbd4aee69bfe7f93.jpg"}],"total":3},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870810/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1713263537","background_raw":"https://share